description: Redevelopment of former Middlesex University campus comprising two sites: Site A - Erection of 5 x 4/5 storey blocks comprising 260 flats (50% affordable) with 258 car parking spaces; 1 x A1 unit and associated landscaping; 15 x B1/B8 units ranging between 103 - 323 m2 with 17 parking spaces. Site B - Erection of 4 x B1/B8 units raging between 279 - 472m2 with 2 parking spaces, new boundary fence and gates. 26 shared ownership and 41 key worker flats.
